name: Ye Olde
description: Life is a blessing within the castle walls of Lord Tryndamere's domain. Knights may seek out the blacksmith to purchase their wares or one of many mages for sage advice. And for the adventurous in spirit, the lands of Albion await, their mysteries known only to the fae folk that reside there.

skinlines.name: Albion
skinlines.description: Once the dominion of fallen Elven empires, the vast forests of Albion are now home to kingdoms and brigands and elves and free men in equal measure. There's power to be found in the imperial ruins, should anyone be bold enough to venture deep into the woods to seek itâ€¦

skinlines.name: Medieval
skinlines.description: Hark, ye knights and knaves, for these lands are under the royal protection of the King and Queen! Make way, make way!
